Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Evening’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Evening” game were:
6-2-8-7-4
(six, two, eight, seven, four)
